dc_title_s: Map of the United Kingdom, or, Water itinerary of Great Britain & Ireland : with the adjacent parts of the Continent, from Amsterdam to Paris and Brest : exhibiting the tracks pursued by the packets in their passage to the several outports, and the Continent, thereby presenting an accurate representation of the present state of steam navigation
